<HEADLINE> Cholera Kills 93 in Maputo </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MAPUTO, April 14 (Xinhua) -- At least 93 people have died from
cholera and other forms of acute diarrhoea since February in the
Mozambican capital Maputo, said the city's health director Olivia
Ferreira on Friday.
