Moro Islamic Liberation Front (MILF) in North Lanao Province,
Mindanao, the military confirmed Friday.
</P>
<P>
Military spokesman Rafael Romero told reporters that MILF
rebels have retreated to neighboring South Lanao Province where
they have several satellite camps.
</P>
<P>
