19 government troops, the spokesman added.
</P>
<P>
Camp Bilal is the biggest MILF stronghold to fall this year.
Camp Omar, the second largest MILF encampment fell in February.
</P>
<P>
Romero said the military is ready to crush any attempt by the
MILF to retake Camp Bilal.
</P>
<P>
The MILF, a 15,000-strong Muslim rebel group, has long been
fighting for the establishment of an independent Islamic state in
Mindanao, which the government strongly opposes. 
