<TEXT>
<P>
LUANDA, April 14 (Xinhua) -- Angolan president Jose Eduardo dos
Santos has said that achieving a total and lasting peace in his
country is one of his government's "top priorities", official news
agency Angop reported on Friday.
</P>
<P>
