<HEADLINE> Amway Celebrates Fifth Anniversary In China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 14 (Xinhua) -- Amway Corp., the direct seller of
cosmetics, kitchenware and other household products, yesterday
celebrated the fifth birthday of Amway China Co.
</P>
<P>
