<HEADLINE> Major News Items in Leading Kenyan Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NAIROBI, April 14 (Xinhua) -- The following are major news
items in leading Kenyan newspapers on Friday.
</P>
<P>
Kenya Times:
</P>
<P>
-- Kenya's campaign for a total ban on the international trade
in ivory received a major boost Thursday with the backing of the
European Union at the meeting of the Convention on International
Trade in Endangered Species being held in Kenya's capital Nairobi.
</P>
