Pena netted opening goal in the 16th minute and four minutes
later scored the second goal.
</P>
<P>
Herrera scored El Nacional's only goal in the 26th minute, and
Palmeiras'Argel made it 3-1 in the 41st minute. Alex scored
Palmerira's fourth goal in the 57th minute. 
