<HEADLINE> IT Cooperation Across Straits Promising: Official </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
XIAMEN, April 14 (Xinhua) -- The two sides across the Taiwan
Straits have shared the view of making up for each other's
disadvantages while giving free rein to their advantages in IT
industry so as to sharpen their respective competitive edge for
mutual benefit.
</P>
<P>
The consensus came from participants of a two-day symposium on
the development of IT in the 21st century, a part of the 4th
Xiamen Fair for Export to Taiwan which ended Thursday.
</P>
<P>
