<HEADLINE> Maltese President Meets Chinese Vice Premier </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Valletta, Malta, April 14 (Xinhua) -- Maltese President Guido
de Marco Friday afternoon met with visiting Chinese Vice Premier
Li Lanqing.
</P>
<P>
Guido de Marco said that Malta and China are geographically far
apart, but the Maltese people have always harbored sincere and
friendly feelings towards the Chinese people. He said that Malta
attaches importance to the major role that China plays in
international affairs.
</P>
