with Malta. He said China is willing to make joint efforts with
Malta in a bid to constantly promote the bilateral cooperation in
new areas and with new ways, and thus pushing forward the Sino-
Maltese ties.
</P>
<P>
Li arrived here Friday morning after his official visit to Cuba,
where he also attended the first South Summit. 
